high_descs: Turn around and face the counter by the sink to your right.
Pick up the knife from the counter in front of you.
Turn around and head to the table in front of you.
Slice the bread on the table in front of you.
Turn around and face the fridge in front of you.
Place the knife in the fridge and close it.
Turn around and face the table in front of you.
Take a slice of bread from the table in front of you.
Turn around and face the fridge in front of you.
Put the bread in the fridge and take it out.
Turn left, then face the brown table to your right with the tomato on top of it.
Place the slice of bread on the table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold slice of bread on a brown table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter next to the sink.
Pick up the paring knife on the counter.
Turn around and go to the white table with a loaf of bread.
Slice the loaf of bread on the table.
Turn around to go to the refrigerator.
Place the paring knife inside the freezer.
Turn around and go back to the white table with the bread.
Take one slice of bread.
Turn around and go back to the refrigerator.
Chill the slice of bread in the refrigerator and take it out.
Take the chilled slice of bread to the small black table on the left.
Place the slice of bread next to the large glass.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled slice of bread next to the large glass.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn right to face the counter to the left of the sink, go to the counter.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn around, go forward to the square white table.
Cut the bread on the table into slices.
Turn around, go forward to the fridge.
Put the knife on the bottom shelf of the top compartment of the fridge.
Turn around, go forward to the square white table.
Take a slice of bread from the table.
Turn around, go forward to the fridge.
Put the slice of bread on the upper shelf of the bottom compartment of the fridge. Close then open the fridge door. Take the bread from the fridge.
Turn left go forward to the rectangular white table, turn right to face the black stand on the left of the counter.
Put the slice of bread on the lower right corner of the stand to the right of the cup.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of bread on a stand.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter that is left of the sink.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Turn around and go to the dining table on the other side of the room.
Use the knife to slice up the bread that is on the table.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Put the knife in the fridge.
Turn around and go back to the dining table.
Pick up a slice of the bread.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Put the bread in the fridge to get cold, then take it out.
Turn to the left and go to the small black table at the other side of the room.
Put the bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of bread on a table.
